metadata.name: Sky Goodman- A Natural Bridge to Pompano
metadata.description:
From the terrain itself, a natural Arc was formed. When passing through it, a certain energy emits where the one who who passes through finds themselves bridged to a fictional or perhaps very real Pompano. 

Created with various processes: Photogrammetry, VR sculpting, Videofeedback, Pixelsorting

Rendered in Blender
4k PNG

Sky Goodman in a multi-media artist and poet who draws inspiration from nature, landscape paintings and science fiction literature.
